<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  
  <title>Article Template</title>
  
  <style>
	h1 {
	font-size: 2em;
	font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
	}
    h2 {
	font-size: 1.7em;
	font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
	}
	h3 {
	font-size: 1.4em;
	font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
	}
	h4,
	h5 {
      font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
    }


    p,
	em,
    ul li {
      font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Georgia';
      font-size: 26px; /* Adjust the font size as desired */
    }

    .blue {
      color: blue;
    }

    .orange {
      color: orange;
    }
  
  
  /* Add the CSS for the scroll to top arrow */
    .scroll-to-top {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 20px; /* Adjust the distance from the bottom as needed */
      right: 20px; /* Adjust the distance from the right as needed */
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: #55a6a2;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 40px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
	
	/* Nav bar */
		.navbar {
	  background-color: #439775;
	  overflow: hidden;
	  text-align: center; /* Center the navigation links */
	  display: flex; /* Add flex display */
	  justify-content: center; /* Center the items horizontally */
	}

	.navbar a {
	  display: inline-block;
	  color: black;
	  text-align: center;
	  padding: 14px 16px;
	  text-decoration: none;
	  font-weight: bold;
	  transition: background-color 0.3s;
	  font-family: "League Spartan", sans-serif;
	}

	.navbar a:hover {
	  background-color: #55a6a2;
	  color: white;
	}
	
	
	
	/* Media query for mobile devices */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      body {
        margin-left: 20px;
		background-color: #FFFFFF;
      }
    }
	
    /* Reset default margins and paddings */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Container for the article content */
    .article-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px;
      font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    /* Article title style */
    .article-title {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Article metadata style */
    .article-metadata {
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Article content style */
    .article-content {
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    /* Article image style */
    .article-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Article tags style */
    .article-tags {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Article tag style */
    .article-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-right: 10px;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }

    /* Article footer style */
    .article-footer {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
	
	/* Caption Styling for Photo */
	figcaption {
  font-size: 0.8em;
  font-style: italic;
  text-align: left;
}

img[class="article-image"] {
  border: 1px solid blue; 
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- Add the navigation bar to the top of the page -->
    <div class="navbar">
		<a href="../pages/index.html" style="background-color: #439775;">Home</a>
        <a href="../pages/cv.html" style="background-color: #439775;">CV</a>
        <a href="../pages/blog.html" style="background-color: #439775;">Blog</a>
    </div>
	
	
  <div class="article-container">
    <h1 class="article-title">Article Title</h1>

    <p class="article-metadata">
      Published on June 20, 2023
    </p>

    <figure>
		<img src="{Image URL}" class="article-image">
		<figcaption>
			{Caption Text} <a href="{Image Source URL}" target="_blank">({Image Source Website})</a>
		</figcaption>
	</figure>

    <div class="article-tags">
      <span class="article-tag">#technology</span>
      <span class="article-tag">#programming</span>
      <span class="article-tag">#webdev</span>
    </div>

    <div class="article-content">
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce feugiat nibh eget turpis consequat volutpat. Nam tempus eros et nunc luctus, at auctor risus posuere. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia curae; Phasellus id mauris ac enim faucibus fringilla. Nullam sodales placerat orci, eget scelerisque sem fermentum ac. Nulla malesuada est quis nunc convallis bibendum. Aliquam nec congue mi.</p>

      <p>Phasellus faucibus massa non justo placerat sagittis. Donec scelerisque magna eget urna cursus, a sollicitudin quam aliquam. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Nunc ultricies metus et diam facilisis, eget tincidunt mi semper. Curabitur eu fringilla arcu. Pellentesque pharetra diam vel luctus congue. Etiam sit amet congue dui. Morbi eu eleifend turpis. Nullam venenatis mauris sit amet gravida eleifend.</p>
      
      <!-- Insert your article content here -->

    </div>

    <div class="article-footer">
      Published by Your Name
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Scroll to top icon -->
  <div class="scroll-to-top" onclick="scrollToTop()">
    &#8593; <!-- Up arrow icon -->
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll to top function -->
  <script>
    function scrollToTop() {
      window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
